  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv data-alias=\"gutenberg-content__content\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.indiewire.com/t/denzel-washington/\" id=\"auto-tag_denzel-washington\" data-tag=\"denzel-washington\"\u003eDenzel Washington\u003c/a\u003e is determined to get \u003ca href=\"https://www.indiewire.com/t/ridley-scott/\" id=\"auto-tag_ridley-scott\" data-tag=\"ridley-scott\"\u003eRidley Scott\u003c/a\u003e his long “overdue” \u003ca href=\"https://www.indiewire.com/t/oscar/\" id=\"auto-tag_oscar\" data-tag=\"oscar\"\u003eOscar\u003c/a\u003e. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eWashington, who reunites with Scott for “\u003ca href=\"https://www.indiewire.com/t/gladiator-ii/\" id=\"auto-tag_gladiator-ii\" data-tag=\"gladiator-ii\"\u003eGladiator II\u003c/a\u003e” almost 20 years after 2007’s “American Gangster,” told \u003ca href=\"https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-features/making-of-gladiator-ii-ridley-scott-paul-mescal-1236066080/?utm_medium=social\u0026amp;utm_source=twitter\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eThe Hollywood Reporter\u003c/a\u003e that Scott not having won Best Director is almost criminal. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e“Ridley is overdue,” Washington said. “How can he not have won an Oscar? That doesn’t even make sense. \u003ca href=\"https://www.indiewire.com/news/general-news/denzel-washington-gladiator-ii-gay-kiss-cut-1235065933/\"\u003eI don’t believe it\u003c/a\u003e, actually.”\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eScott’s original 2000 “Gladiator” \u003ca href=\"https://www.indiewire.com/features/craft/watch-ridley-scott-and-his-collaborators-talking-making-gladiator-2-1235068063/\"\u003ewon Best Picture\u003c/a\u003e, with star Russell Crowe winning Best Actor. Scott was up for Best Director, having been nominated in the category previously with “Thelma \u0026amp; Louise” and again with “Black Hawk Down.” Scott has won BAFTA Awards, Golden Globe Awards, and Primetime Emmy Awards, just not an \u003ca href=\"https://www.indiewire.com/t/academy-award/\" id=\"auto-tag_academy-award\" data-tag=\"academy-award\"\u003eAcademy Award\u003c/a\u003e yet.\n\n\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-pmc-adm-ad-id=\"1234633991\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003ch3\u003e\n\t\t\tPopular on IndieWire\t\t\u003c/h3\u003e\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-alias=\"cards__inner\" data-component=\"cards-related-content\" data-collapse-to-xs=\"false\" data-layout=\"inline\" data-size=\"md\" data-spacing=\"s-3\" data-cards-spacing=\"s0\"\u003e \u003cdiv data-alias=\"card__inner\" data-post-id=\"1235069148\" data-component=\"card\" data-has-background=\"false\" data-has-overlay=\"false\" data-layout-size=\"xs\" data-layout=\"sidebar\" data-main-alignment=\"s0\" data-main-spacing=\"s0\" data-media-position=\"\"\u003e\u003cfigure data-component=\"image\" data-alias=\"\" data-ratio=\"sixteenByNine\" data-round=\"false\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.indiewire.com/news/breaking-news/wolfs-director-jon-watts-i-dont-think-there-will-be-sequel-1235069148/\" title=\"\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"\" data-card-index=\"0\" data-post-id=\"1235069148\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://www.indiewire.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Wolfs_Photo_0106.jpg.photo_modal_show_home_large_2x.jpg?w=300\u0026amp;h=168\u0026amp;crop=1\" alt=\"Wolfs\" height=\"168\" width=\"300\" srcset=\"https://www.indiewire.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Wolfs_Photo_0106.jpg.photo_modal_show_home_large_2x.jpg?w=300\u0026amp;h=168\u0026amp;crop=1 3840w, https://www.indiewire.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Wolfs_Photo_0106.jpg.photo_modal_show_home_large_2x.jpg?w=300\u0026amp;h=168\u0026amp;crop=1\u0026amp;resize=300%2C169 300w, https://www.indiewire.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Wolfs_Photo_0106.jpg.photo_modal_show_home_large_2x.jpg?w=300\u0026amp;h=168\u0026amp;crop=1\u0026amp;resize=1024%2C576 1024w, https://www.indiewire.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Wolfs_Photo_0106.jpg.photo_modal_show_home_large_2x.jpg?w=3